title._content: Elm Street Row in Keene New Hampshire

description._content: TITLE Elm Street Row in Keene New Hampshire CREATOR Wardwell, Anne, Keene NH SUBJECT Houses - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION "Much of the atmosphere of Court street carries over to the area between Court and Washington Streets. Here rows of similar and primarily wood houses in vernacular styles of the 1850s to 1900 are closely and evenly spaced along the narrow, curving streets. The proximity of the buildings and their stylistic associations produces a compact neighborhood." PUBLISHER Keene Public Library and the Historical Society of Cheshire County DATE DIGITAL 20090312 DATE ORIGINAL 1975 RESOURCE TYPE slides FORMAT image/jpg RESOURCE IDENTIFIER hsykfok073 RIGHTS MANAGMENT No known copyright restrictions.
